<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" style="font-size: calc(100vw/18.75);">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>投保成功</title>
    <style>
        html {
            font-size: calc(100vw/ 18.75);
            font-family: "微软雅黑";
            color: #222;
            max-width: 750px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        html,
        body {
            height: 100%;
        }
        @media screen and (min-width:750px) {
            html {
                font-size: 21px;
            }
        }
        input[placeholder],
        [placeholder],
        *[placeholder] {
            color: #222 !important;
        }
        input {
            -webkit-appearance: none;
            -webkit-border-radius: 0;
            -webkit-user-select: text;
            caret-color: #F76F6F;
        }
        body {
            background: #f0efef;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #222;
            -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -moz-user-select: none;
        }
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .left {
            float: left;
        }

        .right {
            float: right;
        }


        .wrap {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
        }

        .wrap-success {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .wrap-success img {
            width: 4.25rem;
            height: 4.25rem;
            margin: 0.6rem auto;
        }

        .wrap-success p {
            font-weight: bold;
            height: 2rem;
            /* line-height: 2rem; */
        }

        .type {
            font-weight: bold;
            padding-top: 0.6rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;

        }

        .tips {
            color: #e1e1e1;
            line-height: 1.6rem;
            text-align: justify;
            padding-top: 0.4rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.4rem;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: #666666;
        }

        .dan-num {
            padding-top: 0.6rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e1e1e1;
        }

        .dan-num p {
            height: 2rem;
            line-height: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }


        .dan-num p span:nth-child(1) {
            color: #666666;
        }

        .dan-num p span:nth-child(2) {
            color: #000000;
        }

        .wei-common {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 0.6rem;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }


        .wei-common img {
            width: 4.75rem;
            height: 4.75rem;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }



        .wei-common p {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #0c0c0e;
            letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
            padding-top: 1.25rem;
        }

        .baodan p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class='wrap'>
        <div class="wrap-success">
            <img src="../images/success.png" alt="">
            <p>投保申请成功</p>
        </div>
        <div class='type'>
            <span>你已经投保:</span>
            <span>众安保险</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tips">
            <span>温馨提示:</span>
            <span>你的保单已进入审核期，稍后会有工作人员与你核实,请您耐心等待，具体以我的保单显示为准</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dan-num">
            <p>
                <span>投保单号&nbsp;</span>
                <span>A51120225522555</span>
            </p>

            <p>
                <span>被保险人&nbsp;</span>
                <span>魏钦录</span>
            </p>
        </div>


        <div class="wei-common">
            <img src="../images/meihua.png" alt="">
            <p>查看您的保单</p>
        </div>
        <div class="baodan">
            <p>长按或扫描二维码关注美华保险微信公众号</p>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>

</html>